🔴 Critical (blocks demo)

1. Student photos don't load — auth headers missing (just fixed, needs rebuild)
2. No real-time attendance feed — WebSocket connects but the UI doesn't react live when a face is recognized
3. CompreFace is single-instance — one camera freeze kills recognition for all students
4. No attendance confirmation UI — when a student is detected, there's no visual confirmation on the teacher's 
screen

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━


🟠 High Priority (investors will ask)

5. No multi-school/multi-tenant support — everything is one flat database, can't onboard School B without 
breaking School A
6. No dashboard analytics — investors want to see graphs: attendance trends, late arrivals, absent streaks, 
class-level stats
7. Manual attendance fallback is broken — the endpoint exists but the UI doesn't work properly
8. Parent notifications don't actually send — Twilio credentials are placeholder, email (Resend) needs 
verification
9. No student enrollment flow on mobile — teachers can add students but the face registration UX is rough
10. Reports are basic — no exportable PDF/Excel, no per-class breakdown

