🟡 Scale/Production gaps

11. PostgreSQL has no connection pooling — will choke at ~50 concurrent users
12. No camera health monitoring — if a camera goes offline, nobody knows
13. Face recognition threshold hardcoded — no per-school tuning
14. No audit logs — who marked who present, when, from which camera
15. APK hardcoded to local IP — needs a settings screen with the school's server URL

